 647:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			/* The following assertion will fail if a service routine (ISR) for
 648:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			an interrupt that has been assigned a priority above
 649:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			configMAX_SYSCALL_INTERRUPT_PRIORITY calls an ISR safe FreeRTOS API
 650:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			function.  ISR safe FreeRTOS API functions must *only* be called
 651:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			from interrupts that have been assigned a priority at or below
 652:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			configMAX_SYSCALL_INTERRUPT_PRIORITY.
 653:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 
 654:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			Numerically low interrupt priority numbers represent logically high
 655:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			interrupt priorities, therefore the priority of the interrupt must
 656:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			be set to a value equal to or numerically *higher* than
 657:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			configMAX_SYSCALL_INTERRUPT_PRIORITY.
 658:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 
 659:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			Interrupts that	use the FreeRTOS API must not be left at their
 660:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			default priority of	zero as that is the highest possible priority,
 661:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			which is guaranteed to be above configMAX_SYSCALL_INTERRUPT_PRIORITY,
 662:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			and	therefore also guaranteed to be invalid.
 663:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 
 664:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			FreeRTOS maintains separate thread and ISR API functions to ensure
 665:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			interrupt entry is as fast and simple as possible.
 666:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 
 667:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			The following links provide detailed information:
 668:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			http://www.freertos.org/RTOS-Cortex-M3-M4.html
 669:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c **** 			http://www.freertos.org/FAQHelp.html */
